description:
This is the album of christian orthodox and serbian traditional music performed by Brkic Triplets. 2 of them Nada and Slobodan are blind but they have got a God's gift which is their spiritual vision and magnificent voice. By singing they are glorifying God and they never stopped believing that 1 day they will be able to see again. With God's help they wil restore their eyesight by having their eye surgery in San Francisco. Therefore they are collecting donations. As those retina implants are very expensive every donation would be highly appreciated.
If you also want to contribute for these young persons to see this beautiful world please check their youtube video and their website as well for donations and share it with your friends. May God bless you. Let's enjoy in this wonderful music and let's all pray for them.
